headline: Electric Grid Upgrade Set to Strengthen Service and Speed Restoration in Monmouth County
summary: A major upgrade is underway in Monmouth County to improve electric service for thousands of Jersey Central Power & Light (JCP&L) customers. The project includes rebuilding and modernizing a key section of the local power grid to strengthen reliability and reduce the frequency and length of outages.
